A late-bloomer with an old soul. Scavenger of dreams.
His own worst archenemy. An epitome of angst. 🙄

The Count of One-Sided Feelings. Always setting himself up for heartbreaks - The heartbreaker & heartbreakee in one package. 💔

Just a lonesome man who may be better off alone. Or perhaps, destined to be.
Again and again, lost in a loop of his feeble-minded fantasies, and incorrigible imaginations. 🎭🤦🏻‍♂️

Following people who in most cases, don't follow back.😌
